# Triple License Notice

**AEGIS-MESH** is released under a triple-license model. Different parts of the repository are governed by different licenses. By contributing to or using this project, you agree to the terms of the applicable license for each part.

### 1. Software, Firmware, and Associated Data (MIT License)

All software code, firmware code, scripts, configuration files, and associated data files (e.g., `.py`, `.rs`, `.c`, `.h`, `.json`, `.toml`, `.yaml`) contained within the `crates/`, `firmware/`, `software/`, and root directories (unless otherwise specified) are licensed under the **MIT License**.

### 2. Hardware Designs (CERN-OHL-S-2)

All hardware designs, including schematics, PCB layouts, mechanical CAD models, and associated hardware description files (e.g., `.kicad_sch`, `.kicad_pcb`, `.step`, `.stl`, `.brd`, `.sch`) contained within the `hardware/` and `mechanical/` directories are licensed under the **CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal**.

### 3. Documentation (CC BY 4.0)

All documentation, guides, theory papers, diagrams, and assets (e.g., `.md`, `.pdf`, `.png`, `.svg`) contained within the `docs/`, `media/`, and `legal/` directories (unless explicitly stating otherwise) are licensed under the **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License**.

