1.18 "Product" means any tangible product or device, or any part thereof, which incorporates, or which is based on, the Licensed Material.

1.19 "Reciprocity" means the obligation to make available the Source of Licensed Modules that are used in a Product under the conditions set out in Clause 4.

1.20 "Share" means to provide copies of the Licensed Material or Licensed Source to any third party.

1.21 "Source" means the human-readable form of the Licensed Material, including all Design Files, associated software, and other materials needed to understand, modify, and manufacture the hardware design, or any part thereof.

