5.1 If You Contribute modifications to the Licensed Source to the Licensor, You grant to the Licensor, and to any recipient of the Licensed Source, a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free licence to use, reproduce, modify, display, perform, sublicense, and distribute Your Contributions.

5.2 By Contributing modifications to the Licensed Source, You represent that You are the owner of the intellectual property rights in the Contributions, or that You are authorised to grant the licences set out in Clause 5.1.

